ont-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot; 0px=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot;&gt;安报全媒体记者 付玉摄&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot; 0px=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 目前，欧阳程程同学住院在&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot;&gt;安庆市立医院新院区血液内科。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;在朋友圈得知这一线索后，6月19日晚11时许，安报全媒体记者第一时间赶往市立医院东院区，核实了解事件相关情况。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot; 0px=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 记者到达医院后，联系上欧阳程程的家长。欧阳程程的父亲欧国根告诉记者，欧阳程程发病比较急，现急需B型血小板和血浆。特别感谢广大热心人士在朋友圈转发来帮助欧阳程程，希望孩子能度过这次难关。&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0