&quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　▼纽西兰专门为蓝企鹅设计的地下通道&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 14px/25px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;img width=&quot;409&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; height: auto; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%;&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.zggyw.org/uploadfile/2018/0806/20180806113038750.gif&quot; original=&quot;/uploadfile/2018/0806/20180806113038750.gif&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 14px/25px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　▼德国高速公路上的野生动物绿色桥梁&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 14px/25px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;img width=&quot;529&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; height: auto; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; vertical-align: bottom; display: block;