ize-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;img width=&quot;530&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; height: auto; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%;&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.zggyw.org/uploadfile/2018/0806/20180806113040624.jpeg&quot; original=&quot;/uploadfile/2018/0806/20180806113040624.jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 14px/25px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　▼加拿大亚伯达的动物桥&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 14px/25px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;img width=&quot;517&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; height: auto; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%;&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.zggyw.org/uploadfile/2018/0806/20180806113041210.jpeg&quot; original=&quot;/uploadfile/2018/0806/20180806113041210.jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 14px/25px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　▼美国蒙大拿州的动物桥&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 14px/25px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;img width=&quot;548&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; height: auto; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%;&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.zggyw.org/uploadfile/2018/0806/20180806113041304.jpeg&quot; original=&quot;/uploadfile/2018/0806/20180806113041304.jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 14px/25px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　▼华盛顿哥伦比亚河中的鲑鱼通道&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 14px/25px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;img width=&quot;553&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; height: auto; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; vertical-align: bottom; display: block; max-width: 100%;&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.zggyw.org/uploadfile/2018/0806/20180806113041715.jpeg&quot; original=&quot;/uploadfile/2018/0806/20180806113041715.jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 14px/25px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　人类占用了动物的生存空间，给它们留出一些安全通道很正常。如果世界上多一些为动物修建的桥梁、通道，每年死于车祸的动物一定会大大减少。我们身边也有一些动物车祸高发路段，真希望动物桥梁能够早日建起来!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1,0,0,1561544967,1561544967),(213,'暴雨导致桂林全州县18万人受灾 已有1人死亡',12,'','图为洪水救灾现场。　钟欣　摄　　6月8日晚至9日上午，广西桂林市全州县部分乡镇出现暴雨，局部地区出现大暴雨到特大暴雨。据当地政府初步...','','/article/20190626/5d134965602d2.jpg','&lt;p style=&quot;font: 16px/36px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; id=&quot;{EA1D62F5-6278-4E66-8022-68B77608FA5C}&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; width: 540px; height: 404px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 740px;&quot; src=&quot;/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190626/1561545057.jpg&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; original=&quot;/uploadfile/2019/0610/20190610111852993.jpg&quot; sourcename=&quot;本地文件&quot; sourcedescription=&quot;编辑提供的本地文件&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 16px/36px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: navy; font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;图为洪水救灾现场。　钟欣　摄&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 16px/36px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　6月8日晚至9日上午，广西桂林市全州县部分乡镇出现暴雨，局部地区出现大暴雨到特大暴雨。据当地政府初步统计，截至9日下午17时，全州县强降雨导致18万人受灾，造成1人死亡，1人失联，直接经济损失约4.6亿元。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 16px/36px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: navy; font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;&lt;img title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; id=&quot;{03B18F19-48C5-4B49-9F6C-26E1850D2CA5}&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; width: 540px; height: 400px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; vertical-align: middle; display: inline; max-width: 740px;&quot; src=&quot;/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190626/1561545057.jpg&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; original=&quot;/uploadfile/2019/0610/20190610111852213.jpg&quot; sourcename=&quot;本地文件&quot; sourcedescription=&quot;编辑提供的本地文件&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 16px/36px 楷体; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: navy; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: navy; font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;图为交警在摆放安全通行提示牌。　钟欣 摄&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 16px/36px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　此次强降雨天气造成全州县龙水镇、才湾镇、绍水镇、庙头镇等乡镇不同程度受灾，多个乡镇发生山洪，农作物被淹，道路毁坏严重。全州县委、县政府于6月9日上午9时组织启动洪涝灾害二级应急响应，全县各级各部门立即行动起来投入到抗洪抢险中。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 16px/36px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; id=&quot;{D64866C2-B35F-4A2B-B445-2878264A654E}&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; width: 405px; height: 540px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; vertical-align: middle; display: inline; max-width: 740px;&quot; src=&quot;/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190626/1561545057.jpg&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; original=&quot;/uploadfile/2019/0610/20190610111852396.jpg&quot; sourcename=&quot;本地文件&quot; sourcedescription=&quot;编辑提供的本地文件&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 16px/36px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: navy; font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;图为消防在转移被困群众。　钟欣 摄&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 16px/36px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　桂林市水文水资源局9日发布消息，据水文监测，过去24小时，桂林市普降小到中雨，龙胜、资源、全州等县降大暴雨到特大暴雨，日雨量超过200毫米的站点4个，100～200毫米的站点37个，日雨量较大的有龙胜县三门镇双江村279.5毫米、全州县才湾镇才湾新村251.0毫米、资源县中峰镇大源村180.0毫米。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 16px/36px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: navy; font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;&lt;img title=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; id=&quot;{305C4EE1-F623-4165-9251-0767BF067169}&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; width: 540px; height: 364px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; vertical-align: middle; display: inline; max-width: 740px;&quot; src=&quot;/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190626/1561545058.jpg&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; original=&quot;/uploadfile/2019/0610/20190610111853511.jpg&quot; sourcename=&quot;本地文件&quot; sourcedescription=&quot;编辑提供的本地文件&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 16px/36px 楷体; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; color: navy; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: navy; font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;图为消防在转移被困群众。　钟欣 摄&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 16px/36px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　受强降雨影响，湘江支流万乡河、古宜河支流六漫河、资江等河流出现了1～4.4米的涨水过程。当前万乡河龙水水文站、六漫河三门水文站等4站已超警0.05～2.25米，龙水水文站已出现历史最高水位。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 16px/36px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　据当地政府初步统计，截至9日下午17时，全州县因强降雨导致灾情严重，受灾人口18万人，转移安置人口8380人，因强降雨造成1人死亡，1人失联；农作物受灾面积7.5万亩，房屋倒塌87间，道路损毁187处，桥梁涵洞损毁117处，水利、电力、供水、网络、通讯等设施损毁严重，经初步测算，直接经济损失约4.6亿元。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font: 16px/36px &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, Arial; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　据桂林气象部门预计，9日晚桂林北部大雨到暴雨、局部大暴雨，中南部暴雨到大暴雨、局部特大暴雨，并可能伴有短时雷雨大风等强对流天气；10日白天中北部大雨转小雨，局部大到暴雨。(欧惠兰 赵琳露)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1,0,0,1561545061,1561545061);
